Issue_Desc: Herbicide overspray has damaged or killed every tree within ~3 feet of CE boundary.

Issue: Bare Areas, Low Stem Vigor/Height & Density
Issue_Desc: Old road still looks like a road. Only a couple stems alive in this area. Low herbaceous growth as well but no sign of mowing or vehicular traffic.
Treat_Desc: Relieved soil compaction mechanicall (O & A horizons)y. Planted 20 1 gal containers (QUPH, BENI). Seeded with cool season CC & perm species.
